<subSubSection id="BB8C65091067CE3FC38171F0C2DD95BE" pageId="12" pageNumber="27" type="type material">
<paragraph id="95F51683B7DA49DB82E94A3B95491DB0" pageId="12" pageNumber="27">Type material.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="386DC66306185130B57D3E1580FB8814" pageId="12" pageNumber="27">
1 M holotype (UCAM), Taznakht (30.51853°, -7.02595°), Ouarzazate, Morocco. Paratypes: 1 M, 2 F (UCAM), 1 M, 1 F (ZMH), 2 M, 1 F (MNHN), all from the same locality; 1 M (ZMH), 
<normalizedToken id="6324737BE44A6B4E2CC3D231920E7C6D" originalValue="Aït">Ait</normalizedToken>
Bassou; 2 F juv. (ZMH), 
<normalizedToken id="E124F83EFDDA259F493D126C1351B865" originalValue="Aït">Ait</normalizedToken>
Ounzar Oulad Aissa; 1 M (ZMH), near Agdez; 1 M (ZMH), Oulad Hlal. The ZMH accession number for all paratypes is A7/03.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="E73C571FA48BD384C85BA4F2E3F4CEA3" pageId="12" pageNumber="27" type="distribution">
